<note id="fs-idm247865104" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm475590960"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 7.13 World War II: Military</para>
<para id="fs-idm475663840"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm247925824"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 7M Explain the causes and effects of the victory of the United States and its allies over the Axis Powers</para>
<para id="fs-idm481522032"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 7.3.III.D</para>
<para id="fs-idm475047776"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
